{"tid":2224572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（神奇女俠）亞美尼亞千年古墓挖掘出土　「亞馬遜戰士」重見天日","createTime":"2020-09-30T15:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T05:39:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ec10b84bbb67561aab8af74469a79bbffce820bf","tid":2224572,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"日前考古團隊在亞美尼亞（Armenia）一座千年古墓內，發現一具骨骸，經過鑑定及從陪葬品推斷，確認該骨骸主人為生於鐵器時代的女性；加上考古學家根據骨骸上的傷痕，推測死者可能是名戰士，根據這些線索，學者相信自己找到了傳說中的「亞馬遜女戰士」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/02/2277420-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F02%2F2277420-XXL.jpg&h=48c9c4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲考古學家在亞美尼亞一座千年古墓裡，發現一具「亞馬遜女戰士」的骨骸。（示意圖／unsplash）<br />\n<br />\n由亞美尼亞國家科學院考古學家韋迪安（Anahit Khudaverdyan）領導的研究團隊，日前在洛里省（Lori）發現一名女性骨骸，根據鑑定，該名女子生於西元前6到8世紀，死亡年齡約為20多歲。<br />\n<br />\n考古學家依據骨骸身邊的陪葬品及「彎曲身體」的埋葬方式判斷，推斷該名女性應是貴族身分，不過，再經過更詳細的考察、檢後，更多資訊一一浮上檯面，考古學家發現，骨骸上傷痕累累，後腦有遭受重擊的痕跡，加上研究人員發現，她的胸肌、三角肌等肌肉群組非常發達，推測應該是長期練習拉弓造成，讓考古學家相信，這極有可能是熟悉射箭、騎馬的戰士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/02/2277424-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F02%2F2277424-XXL.jpg&h=4bcfffb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲綜合諸多考古線索，這具骨骸被推斷為女戰士。（示意圖／unsplash）<br />\n<br />\n考古團隊認為，這名女戰士是在戰場上被劍擊中身亡，而她也是亞美尼亞高山地區洛里省發現的第2名女戰士。據媒體報導，美國DC漫畫《神力女超人》就是以古希臘神話中亞馬遜人的形象為基礎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx?NewsID=646107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fampnews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D646107&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kynjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=01669c26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fampnews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D646107&h=3a4ea2b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx?NewsID=646107</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.best-wallpaper.net/wallpaper/iphone/1706/Wonder-Woman-war-riding-horse-Gal-Gadot_iphone_320x480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.best-wallpaper.net%2Fwallpaper%2Fiphone%2F1706%2FWonder-Woman-war-riding-horse-Gal-Gadot_iphone_320x480.jpg&h=67f92bc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10ca95bd2b028375621448415e6e0938f6cbe4cd","tid":2224572,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff95de9230e71ba705754dc57b7ce8f5a643667","tid":2224572,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190930/12aa42e971de4607834603872e680a0e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190930%2F12aa42e971de4607834603872e680a0e.jpeg&h=c211d664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ficquotes.com/images/quotes/diana-prince-wonder-woman-369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fficquotes.com%2Fimages%2Fquotes%2Fdiana-prince-wonder-woman-369.jpg&h=929ccc5a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}